        "timestamp": "2019-12-17 19:52:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nThis is backing out a change I'd made to run merge builds with a profile (dependency-list) that will generate a list of third party dependencies.  Unfortunately, the plugin I'm using has to run at the top level pom, and runs before any modules are processed ... meaning that if any new\nmodules are added, the plugin will consider that new module a missing dependency.\n\nInstead, I'll have to look into running a separate job that dependency list (possibly as a post build script)",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
